data.description: Showings start Friday April 26th 10am. Great Bi-level home on a large lot with no HOA! This 3 bed 2 bath home with an attached single car garage and a detached oversized single car garage is a fit for any buyer. Granite counter tops, 42" maple cabinets, hickory floors in the kitchen. Life-proof wood laminate in main living areas and life-proof carpeting on stairs both new in 2020. Two separate living rooms, one up and one down. Large deck off the kitchen new in 2020. Additional updates: Whole house fan w/ wall controls 2022, blown-in attic insulation 2023, new roof 2020, nest thermostat 2023, solar panels 2023, deck off of detached garage 2022, new sewer line 2022, raised garden bed 2022, interior paint April 2024, laundry room update April 2024, New banister shelves and railing in entry 2024. Top this one off with RV/boat parking and yes, it's in a cul-de-sac.
